            <p>
                Sweet Crumbs Bakery is a family-owned bakery located in Johannesburg,
                South Africa. Established in 2018, the bakery began as a small
                home-based business with a passion for creating fresh, high-quality
                baked goods. Through dedication, creativity, and exceptional customer
                service, Sweet Crumbs Bakery has grown into a trusted local bakery
                serving individuals, families, schools, and businesses.
            </p>

            <p>
                We take pride in preparing every product with premium ingredients,
                ensuring freshness, great taste, and beautiful presentation.
                From artisan breads to custom celebration cakes, our bakery is
                committed to making every occasion memorable.
